## 2. Discoveries

**Schema:**
```json
{
  "title": "Discovery",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": { "type": "string" },
    "name": { "type": "string" },
    "description": { "type": "string" },
    "region": { "type": "string" },
    "discovered_by": { "type": "string" }, // player name or ID
    "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" }
  },
  "required": ["id", "name", "region", "discovered_by"]
}
```

**Example:**
```json
{
  "id": "region_5_peak",
  "name": "Mountain Peak of Region 5",
  "description": "The highest point in Region 5, first known to explorers.",
  "region": "Region 5",
  "discovered_by": "Player123",
  "date": "2024-04-27"
}
```

**Validation Rules:**
- `id`, `name`, `region`, `discovered_by` required.
- `date` must be valid date string if provided.

