## 3. World Events

**Schema:**
```json
{
  "title": "WorldEvent",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": { "type": "string" },
    "name": { "type": "string" },
    "description": { "type": "string" },
    "trigger": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "type": { "type": "string" }, // e.g., "date", "achievement"
        "value": { "type": "string" } // date string or achievement ID
      },
      "required": ["type", "value"]
    },
    "effects": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": { "type": "string" }
    }
  },
  "required": ["id", "name", "trigger"]
}
```

**Example:**
```json
{
  "id": "eclipse_event",
  "name": "Eclipse of the Ancients",
  "description": "A rare celestial event affecting gameplay.",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "date",
    "value": "2024-12-21"
  },
  "effects": ["Increase monster spawn rate", "Unlock special quest"]
}
```

**Validation Rules:**
- `id`, `name`, `trigger.type`, `trigger.value` required.
- `effects` optional.

