## 5. NPC Schedules

**Schema:**
```json
{
  "title": "NPCSchedule",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "npc_id": { "type": "string" },
    "schedule": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "time": { "type": "string" }, // "HH:MM"
          "location": { "type": "string" },
          "activity": { "type": "string" }
        },
        "required": ["time", "location"]
      }
    }
  },
  "required": ["npc_id", "schedule"]
}
```

**Example:**
```json
{
  "npc_id": "npc_001",
  "schedule": [
    { "time": "08:00", "location": "market", "activity": "sell_goods" },
    { "time": "12:00", "location": "tavern", "activity": "rest" },
    { "time": "18:00", "location": "home", "activity": "sleep" }
  ]
}
```

**Validation Rules:**
- Each schedule entry must have `time` and `location`.

