## 6. Factions

**Schema:**
```json
{
  "title": "Faction",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": { "type": "string" },
    "name": { "type": "string" },
    "description": { "type": "string" },
    "alignment": { "type": "string", "enum": ["friendly", "neutral", "hostile"] },
    "members": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": { "type": "string" } // member NPC IDs
    }
  },
  "required": ["id", "name"]
}
```

**Example:**
```json
{
  "id": "faction_knights",
  "name": "Order of the Silver Knight",
  "description": "A chivalrous faction dedicated to protecting the realm.",
  "alignment": "friendly",
  "members": ["npc_001", "npc_005"]
}
```

**Validation Rules:**
- `id`, `name` required.
- `alignment` defaults to "neutral" if omitted.

